code: @Override public String toString() {     return "Event{id='" + id + "', type='" + type + "', data='" + data + "'}". }

@Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o)         return true.     if (!(o instanceof Event))         return false.     Event other = (Event) o.     return Objects.equals(id, other.id) && Objects.equals(type, other.type) && data.equals(other.data). }
@Override public int hashCode() {     int result = Objects.hashCode(id).     result = 31 * result + Objects.hashCode(type).     result = 31 * result + data.hashCode().     return result. }
